{"tid":580914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全國兩會】李克強：修憲刪國家主席任期限制 有利習核心「集中統一領導」","createTime":"2018-03-05T01:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T22:30:59.000Z","uid":73262,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"050b9e6aef184cdcb2eafac393362fe08b30c039","tid":580914,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T01:41:32.000Z","msg":"全國兩會其中一個重要議程，是修改憲法，其中刪除國家主席、國家副主席「連續任職不得超過兩屆」條文，是外界最關注的焦點。李克強在政府工作報告中指出，指憲法修正案中刪去國家主席任期限制的字眼，是「有利維護以習近平為核心的黨中央權威和集中統一領導，有利加強和完善國家領導體制」。<br />\n李克強又稱，在徵求意見和在基層調研過程中，「好多地區、部門和黨員幹部群眾一致呼籲，修改憲法中國家主席任職期限的有關規定」，他更稱「大家一致認為，目前黨章對中央軍事委員會主席，都沒有作出『連續任職不得超過兩屆』的規定。<br />\n李克強所指刪除國家主席任期有利維護習核心的說法，是全國人大發言人張業遂，昨日在記者會上首次提出。<br />\n<br />\n中国人民的驕傲  高呼【萬歲， 萬歲萬萬歲喇】<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa5d4e2950a8c68fee2c98ea380cb36beb19e9d","tid":580914,"uid":40216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T01:42:57.000Z","msg":"周恩來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f583639a352979741165d6ac24c2d7f42cc3b3","tid":580914,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aa5d4e2950a8c68fee2c98ea380cb36beb19e9d","tid":580914,"uid":40216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T01:42:57.000Z","msg":"周恩來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T01:57:15.000Z","msg":"周恩來生CANCER之後毛澤東點醫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cbe524d76fbe623c9c74ca20ec3daf8803a7e46","tid":580914,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T02:33:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>周恩來&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/lihkg/dog1.gif&quot; cl